Title: A Thousand Deaths
Plot: Vic and the Strike Team use their leverage on the One-Niners to track down anyone involved with the cop killings.  Their hunt leads them down an unexpected path with the Russian mob.  Monica puts pressure on the team to come clean about any of their dealings with Antwon.  Dutch and Claudette investigate a gang shooting and soon realize their key witness is close to the Barn, and has something to hide.
